instructions: Place the dinner place in the center of the table cloth.
Place the salad plate on the dinner plate.
Place the folded napkin on top of the salad plate.
Add a wine glass to the top right corner of the table cloth.
Stick a water glass next to the wine glass to the bottom ride side.
Add a salad fork to the left side of the plate.
Place a dinner fork to the right side of the salad fork.
Place a dinner knife on the right side of the table cloth.
Put a soup spoon to the right of the dinner knife.
